id: The Derivatives (DER) Domain covers many of the concepts that are common to derivative instruments, including but not limited to options, futures, forwards, swaps, and a wide range of other derivatives. This ontology provides metadata about the Derivatives Domain and its contents.
name: The Derivatives (DER) Domain covers many of the concepts that are common to derivative instruments, including but not limited to options, futures, forwards, swaps, and a wide range of other derivatives. This ontology provides metadata about the Derivatives Domain and its contents.

id: The 'all' ontology for DER is provided for convenience for FIBO users.  This ontology does not add new assertions, but imports all of the Production (Released) ontologies that comprise the FIBO Foundations (FND), Business Entities (BE), Financial Business and Commerce (FBC), Indices and Indicators (IND), Securities (SEC), and Derivatives (DER) domains, including all individuals.
